DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nAges: 0-6
 0 months\\nCategory: Play\\n\\nRepresentatives from the Philharmonic Socie
 ty will be visiting to give a performance and share some information on h
 ow strings\, woodwinds\, brass\, and percussion create beautiful music. I
 t’s a fun\, informative way for kids (and also grown-ups) to learn abou
 t various instruments.\nTIME: 11 AM Included in museum admission. Space i
 s limited! Book your tickets now. \n*Members do not require a reservat
 ion.\n*Events and dates are subject to change.\\n\\nMore info: https://www
 .pretendcity.org/events/meet-the-instrument-2/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/meet-the-instrument-2/
