DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nAges: 0-6
 0 months\\nCategory: Play\\n\\nWe’re opening the city just for toddlers
 ! \nClimb\, dance\, problem-solve\, and pretend your way through our mini
 ature world\, designed to support movement\, connection\, and big developm
 ental leaps. \nDesigned for children 19 months to 3 years. \nThis prog
 ram is exclusively for toddlers and their caregivers. No older siblings\,
  please. \n*Registration is required\, including members*\nEvery Monday!
 \n9:00 AM – 10:30 AM\nFee: $12 per person  \nGENERAL PUBLIC REGISTER H
 ERE\nMEMBERS REGISTER HERE\\n\\nMore info: https://www.pretendcity.org/eve
 nts/toddler-town-3/2026-03-30/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/toddler-town-3/2026-03-30/
