UID:c41a16a47e8033d659d2bf5a7728413f@family-events-agent
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:children,play,toddler,museum,family
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nAges: 0-6
 0 months\\nCategory: Play\\n\\nGet ready to rock\, roll\, sway\, sing\, an
 d bop! Because we’re bringing back Kidstock Music &amp\; Arts Festival! 
 Enjoy live musical performances throughout the week and explore a mix of m
 usical styles! Because of your generosity during Igniting Potential\, Kids
 tock will be bigger\, brighter\, and more hands-on than ever!\n3/31\n\n11 
 am: The Rhythm Child Network\n2:30 pm: Pacific Dance\n\n\n4/1\n\n11 am: As
 hley Mills Monaghan\n2:30 pm: Jukie Davie\n\n\n4/2\n\n11 am &amp\; 2:30 pm
  DrumatiX\n\n\n4/3\n\n11 am: Conga Kids\n2:30 pm: Philharmonic Society’s
  Orange County Youth Symphony musicians\n\n\n4/4\n\n11 am: SoCal Drum Part
 y\n1 pm: Bhangra by Nature\n\n4/5 CLOSED for Easter\nWeek 2\n4/7\n\n11 am 
 &amp\; 2:30 pm Fouta Toro West African Dance and Drum Ensemble\n\n4/8\n\n1
 1 am: Backhaus Dance\n2:30 pm: Mommy Center Music\n\n4/9\n\n11 am: WeBreak
  Hip-Hop Dance Company\n2:30 pm: Ufirst Artist\n\n4/10\n\n11 am &amp\; 2:3
 0 pm: Platinum Performing Arts\n\n4/11\n\n11 am: El Centro Cultural de Mé
 xico\n1 pm: The Portobellas\n2:30 pm: Kymberly Stewart\n\nThis exhibit is 
 included in museum admission. Space is limited! Book your tickets now.
  \nEvent DetailsMarch 31 – April 11Performance times vary by daySpring 
 Break hours: Tuesday–Sunday\, 10 am–4 pmClosed April 5 for EasterEvent
 s subject to change.\nFAQs\nIs Kidstock included with admission?Yes. All p
 erformances are included with regular museum admission.\nWhat ages is Kids
 tock best for?The festival is designed for children ages 0–8 and their f
 amilies.\nDo performances happen every day?Yes. Live music or dance perfor
 mances take place daily during the festival\, except when the museum is cl
 osed.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.pretendcity.org/events/kidstock/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/kidstock/
