SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:children,play,toddler,museum,family
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nAges: 0-6
 0 months\\nCategory: Play\\n\\nDedicated to children 18 months and younger
 \, Pretend City hosts TWO Baby Steps programs a month on the first Tuesday
  and second Sunday. This program is a great way to socialize your little o
 ne and offers new learning opportunities in a safe space. This is perfect 
 for first-time parents who can engage with one another\, learn about other
  resources in the community\, all while playing without older children in 
 the museum. \nThis event features a story time at 8:45 am in Orange Plaza
  and finishes off the morning in our grand exit parade. \nNO OLDER SIBLIN
 GS PLEASE \n\n8-9:30 am \n$12 per adult (non-member) \n0-18 months are 
 free \nMembers are free \n\nRSVP HERE\\n\\nMore info: https://www.prete
 ndcity.org/events/baby-steps-3/2026-04-07/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/baby-steps-3/2026-04-07/
