 ine\n\nDevelopmental Screenings:\n⦁ Check your child’s developmental m
 ilestones and receive valuable insights into their growth\n⦁ Vision Scre
 enings: Detect early signs of vision issues to ensure your child’s eyes 
 are healthy.\n⦁ Dental Screenings: Keep your child’s smile bright and 
 healthy with a free dental check-up.\n⦁ Social-Emotional Screenings: As
 sess your child’s emotional well-being and get support for their mental 
 health.\n⦁ And more!\nWhy Attend?\nEarly Detection: Catch potential heal
 th concerns early\, allowing for timely intervention and support.\nFree Se
 rvices: Access these important health screenings at no cost to you.\nExper
 t Guidance: Receive advice and resources from trained professionals to sup
 port your child’s development and health.\nPLUS\, your child can earn a 
